<section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="title">Powerful Features</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">
            Everything you need to build and test your API responses with confidence
        </p>
        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Real-time Preview</h3>
                <p class="card-description">
                    See your JSON objects in real-time as you type, with instant validation and error highlighting to catch issues early.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Ready-made Templates</h3>
                <p class="card-description">
                    Start quickly with pre-built JSON templates for common API responses like users, products, pagination, and more.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Code Generation</h3>
                <p class="card-description">
                    Generate API client code for your favorite language or framework with one click, supporting TypeScript, Python, Ruby, and more.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Schema Validation</h3>
                <p class="card-description">
                    Define JSON schemas and validate your responses against them to ensure consistency and correctness in your API design.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">API Mocking</h3>
                <p class="card-description">
                    Create temporary endpoints that return your mock data, perfect for frontend development before the backend is ready.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3 class="card-title">Version History</h3>
                <p class="card-description">
                    Track changes to your API design with automatic versioning, allowing you to roll back to previous versions when needed.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about-section {
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: var(--light-bg);
        color: var(--white-text);
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .title {
        font-size: 4.8rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 4.8rem 0 2rem 0;
    }
    .subtitle {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 4.8rem ;
    }
    .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(34rem, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
        background: var(--dark-bg);
        padding: 2.8rem;
        height: 34rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #262626;
        text-align: left;
    }
    .card-title {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .card-description {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
</style>